headline: Profluent Announces Multi-Year Collaboration with Corteva to Accelerate Sustainable, AI-Powered Crop Innovation
summary: EMERYVILLE, Calif., October 06, 2025--Profluent Bio, a pioneer in generative AI for protein design, announced today a strategic collaboration with Corteva, a global leader in agricultural sciences and solutions. Under the collaboration, the companies will use artificial intelligence (AI) and gene editing to deliver a new generation of more sustainable, resilient crops.

headline: SpinCo? Iowans say Corteva should consider 'Pioneer' when naming a new seed business
summary: With Corteva planning to separate seed, crop protection into new companies next year, some say it should consider 'Pioneer' name for seed spinoff.
